a guy like me down?

50:44.960 --> 50:46.439
Well, no.

50:50.520 --> 50:55.275
- You look so good.
- Look, open that up. Open it.

50:55.920 --> 50:58.115
- For me?
- I think so.

50:59.280 --> 51:02.511
It's nothing much,
you know, nothing.

51:07.280 --> 51:08.759
See what's written on the back?

51:08.840 --> 51:10.114
On the back?

51:11.920 --> 51:15.674
- Always.
- "Always." It's beautiful, Tony!

51:17.160 --> 51:19.196
Mama is still working
in the factory...

51:19.280 --> 51:21.316
